+Updated stale node tests that depended on live RPC endpoints to use deterministic EIP-1193 mock transports. The fork tests now cover the current fetchForkAnchor behavior without network access, and the P256 precompile gas assertion matches the corrected implementation. Removed the obsolete getBlockNumber snapshot via `pnpm test:run -u`.
