+- src/createTevmNode.spec.ts:226 - Updated fork.chainId/common priority test to use the mock fork transport.
+- src/createTevmNode.spec.ts:244 - Updated auto-detected fork chain id test to use mock RPC chain id 10.
+- src/createTevmNode.spec.ts:329 - Updated latest fork block tag test to use the mock fork anchor transport.
+- src/createTevmNode.spec.ts:390 - Updated P256 precompile expected gas from 3450n to 6900n.
+- src/createTevmNode.coverage.spec.ts:7 - Added deterministic fork RPC block/transport fixtures for coverage tests.
+- src/createTevmNode.coverage.spec.ts:95 - Updated fork transport function test to use the mock transport.
+- src/createTevmNode.coverage.spec.ts:115 - Updated specific fork blockTag test to use the mock transport.
+- src/createTevmNode.coverage.spec.ts:238 - Updated forkTransport deepCopy test to use the mock transport.
+- src/createTevmNode.coverage.spec.ts:327 - Updated fork/cache coverage test to use the mock transport.
